description:
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for motivated, dynamic professional staff nurse to join the Fareham 2 Community Care Team based in Segensworth.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Variable hours available,to include working 1 in 4 weekends.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our Community Care Teams visit people in their own homes, care homes, and in a clinical setting, offering treatment and support to a wide variation of patients, carers and families.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We cover 5 surgeries in the local area.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Training and development opportunities are available to enhance your current skill base.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Access to a vehicle and possession of a full driving license is essential.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Further enquiries please contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Amanda Bostwick Community Matron on 01489 554962&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Happy to talk flexible working&lt;/strong&gt;-&lt;strong&gt; all requests for flexible and part time working will be considered.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Follow us on Facebook and on Twitter:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;facebook.com/SouthernHealthNHS&lt;/p&gt;
